name: r-blastula
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.3.2' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-blastula
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/blastula_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/blastula/blastula_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: cccf7620aeb2c278b731bece72b3c327f29dd1743a6eabd0cd7847b4ba999520

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-base64enc >=0.1_3
    - r-commonmark >=1.7
    - r-curl >=4.3
    - r-digest
    - r-dplyr >=0.8.3
    - r-fs >=1.3.1
    - r-getpass >=0.2_2
    - r-here >=0.1
    - r-htmltools >=0.4.0
    - r-httr >=1.4.0
    - r-jsonlite >=1.6
    - r-magrittr >=1.5
    - r-mime >=0.6
    - r-rlang >=0.4.1
    - r-rmarkdown
    - r-stringr >=1.4.0
    - r-uuid >=0.1_2
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-base64enc >=0.1_3
    - r-commonmark >=1.7
    - r-curl >=4.3
    - r-digest
    - r-dplyr >=0.8.3
    - r-fs >=1.3.1
    - r-getpass >=0.2_2
    - r-here >=0.1
    - r-htmltools >=0.4.0
    - r-httr >=1.4.0
    - r-jsonlite >=1.6
    - r-magrittr >=1.5
    - r-mime >=0.6
    - r-rlang >=0.4.1
    - r-rmarkdown
    - r-stringr >=1.4.0
    - r-uuid >=0.1_2

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('blastula')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('blastula')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/rich-iannone/blastula
  license: MIT
  summary: Compose and send out responsive HTML email messages that render perfectly across a
    range of email clients and device sizes. Helper functions let the user insert embedded
    images, web link buttons, and 'ggplot2' plot objects into the message body. Messages
    can be sent through an 'SMTP' server, through the 'RStudio Connect' service, or
    through the 'Mailgun' API service <http://mailgun.com/>.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT'
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
